  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The model was revised in early 2026 (modelRevisionDate 2026-02-01); however, the primary boundary-condition dataset carries a dataVintage of 2025-09-15, predating the revision. Re-validation against the updated model build is described as 'planned' but no completed re-validation evidence is present in this package. Full 13-factor assessment performed; decision outcome is Accepted based on assessed factors, but the stale dataset represents an unresolved epistemic gap.",
