      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty for the hemolysis constitutive law has not been assessed. Only the power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger correlation is used; no comparison against alternative models (e.g., Arora, Faghih-Sharp) has been performed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1."
